title: Google Calendar Sync 0.9.3.0 - The one that still works
description:
Google Calendar Sync 0.9.3.0 (one before the April 08 update)

After looking thru the web for a link to the OLD working version of this program, I found it. Here is the one BEFORE it ask you to update and you did and then you said\" damn it, why did I do that\". 

I just un-installed the \"updated\" (broken) version that tells you %d is the error, and reinstalled this version.

-Have Fun
